  "texts": [
    "These issues are foundational to understanding the constraints that affect the performance, generalizability, and fairness of AI models in sensory science.",
    "One of the most pervasive limitations is bias within AI models.",
    "These biases often arise from skewed or homogenous training data, where certain populations or sensory profiles are overrepresented.",
    "As a result, AI systems trained under such conditions may produce inaccurate or culturally insensitive outputs when exposed to diverse real-world data.",
    "In the context of olfaction and gustation, this can lead to misclassification of sensory preferences or failure to predict user responses outside of the training distribution."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}